*sylpheed-claws-1.9.99 (07 Nov 2005)

  07 Nov 2005; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org>
  +sylpheed-claws-1.9.99.ebuild:
  Adding stable candidate 1.9.99 with a few minor changes:
   - remove nls useflag as it's no longer supported by configure (thanks to
     TGL for pointing that out)
   - remove --with-config-dir and --program-suffix options as they are now 
     default upstream 
   - remove einfo about config dir as this is now handled by upstream
     (thanks to TGL for pointing that out)

  23 Oct 2005; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  sylpheed-claws-1.9.15.ebuild:
  Correctly DEPEND on libetpan-0.39. Closes bug #110247, reported by a.l.e
  <xale-gentoo at altern.org>.

