*sylpheed-claws-1.9.13 (13 Aug 2005)

  13 Aug 2005; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org>
  +sylpheed-claws-1.9.13.ebuild:
  New gtk2 version, now uses libetpan for imap, gpgme-0.4 or higher for gpg
  support and optionally uses gnomeprint. Also the spamassassin plugin is now
  optional and the pgpinline plugin is included now (and therefore this
  version blocks the pgpinline package). This is a candidate for unmasking.

